---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10">
    <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-[-10rem] h-[26rem] w-[26rem] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-tg-100/60 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-page py-16 sm:py-24 text-center">
    <p class="badge mx-auto">官方源 · 安全无捆绑 · 持续更新</p>
    <h1 class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-4xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl">
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-tg-500 to-tg-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Telegram 下载</span>｜电脑版 · 安卓 · iOS · Mac 客户端
    </h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-600 sm:text-lg">
      Telegram（中文用户常称<strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">“纸飞机”</strong>“飞机”或<strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">“电报”</strong>）下载导航。
      汇总 Windows 电脑版、安卓 APK、iOS、Mac、Linux 安全下载入口，附简体中文一键设置教程。
    </p>

    <div class="mt-9 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="/windows/" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary">
        <Icon name="windows" class="h-5 w-5" /> Windows 电脑版
      </a>
      <a href="/android/" class="btn btn-lg btn-ghost">
        <Icon name="android" class="h-5 w-5" /> 安卓 APK
      </a>
      <a href="/ios/" class="btn btn-lg btn-ghost">
        <Icon name="apple" class="h-5 w-5" /> iOS / iPhone
      </a>
    </div>

    <dl class="mx-auto mt-12 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
      {[
        { k: '6+', v: '支持平台' },
        { k: '100%', v: '官方源下载' },
        { k: '简体中文', v: '一键设置' },
      ].map((s) => (
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/70 px-3 py-4">
          <dt class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">{s.k}</dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">{s.v}</dd>
        </div>
      ))}
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>
